<BODY lang=EN-US style="tab-interval: .5in">
<DIV class=Section1>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 22pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: TrebuchetMS;
mso-bidi-font-family: TrebuchetMS">VoIP 
Inc.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 22pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: TrebuchetMS;
mso-bidi-font-family: TrebuchetMS">Investor 
Fact Sheet<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><B><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial,Bold;
mso-bidi-font-family: 'Arial,Bold'"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><B><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial,Bold;
mso-bidi-font-family: 'Arial,Bold'">The 
Inside Track on Internet Telephony<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><B><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial,Bold;
mso-bidi-font-family: 'Arial,Bold'"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><B><SPAN 
style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial,Bold; mso-bidi-font-family:
'Arial,Bold'">-- 
Voice over IP (VoIP) is a technology whose time has come. With broadband 
expected soon to reach most computer users, Internet-based telephony is set
for 
explosive growth.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><B><SPAN 
style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial,Bold; mso-bidi-font-family:
'Arial,Bold'"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><B><SPAN 
style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial,Bold; mso-bidi-font-family:
'Arial,Bold'">-- 
VoIP Inc. (OTCBB: VOII) is poised to profit from this new telecom wave
through 
multiple business lines and a unique mix of
services.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><B><SPAN 
style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial,Bold; mso-bidi-font-family:
'Arial,Bold'"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><B><SPAN 
style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial,Bold; mso-bidi-font-family:
'Arial,Bold'">-- 
VOII is currently the only VoIP company offering 911 emergency access
without 
the need for third-party databases.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><B><SPAN 
style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial,Bold; mso-bidi-font-family:
'Arial,Bold'"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><B><SPAN 
style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial,Bold; mso-bidi-font-family:
'Arial,Bold'">-- 
Major units of VOII are already operating in the black. By early 2006, VOII

projects company-wide profitability on overall sales of about $300 
million.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><B><SPAN 
style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial,Bold; mso-bidi-font-family:
'Arial,Bold'"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><B><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial,Bold;
mso-bidi-font-family: 'Arial,Bold'"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><B><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial,Bold;
mso-bidi-font-family: 'Arial,Bold'">Why 
Buy Now<o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY:
Arial"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><SPAN 
style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">Two elements are needed to create
a 
home-run growth stock. One is an industry on the verge of spectacular
growth. 
The other is a company with an edge – such as proprietary products or
unique 
services -- over rivals in that industry. VoIP Incorporated (VOII) fits
this 
description well. Its industry, voice-over-Internet protocol (VoIP), is
just 
starting to take off worldwide and could ultimately replace most
traditional 
telephony. Its edge in this highly competitive area comes from its business
mix, 
which it believes to be unique in the industry.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify;
mso-layout-grid-align: none"><SPAN 
style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">VOII provides VoIP service to
business 
and residential customers, but it enhances that high-growth business with a
wide 
range of related products and services. It sells equipment, designs and
installs 
wireless communications networks, and it performs system integration for 
Internet telephony service providers. It also provides VoIP-based solutions
such 
as hosted VoIP billing, toll-free origination and VoIP termination to
wholesale 
and enterprise customers. This range of activities is both distinctive and 
synergistic. It enables VOII to offer competitively priced packages to
large 
customers with complex telecom needs. And it opens marketing doors, giving
VOII 
units access to other units’ customers</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY:
Arial">.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN:
justify"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 
style="MARGIN: 0in 233.25pt 0pt 3in; TEXT-ALIGN:
justify"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></P>
